title: Vray for Sketchup 2014 + Patch
description:
Vray for Sketchup 2014 + Patch


Requirements:

- Sketchup 2014 already installed and licenced


How to install:

1- Open "vray_demo_20024261_sketchup_2014_win_x86.exe" and follow installation guide.
2- Disable all anti-virus software
3- Unrar with Winrar or Winzip
4- Right click on file > Open as administrator
5- Click next, then next...
6- You're done!

If you are a crappy designer and don't have money to buy the actual license from ChaosGroup then this patch is for you!!!
